title: BRIEF-Australian Government Takeovers Panel Declines To Conduct Proceedings On Application On Keybridge Capital
text:
BRIEF-Australian Government Takeovers Panel Declines To Conduct Proceedings On Application On Keybridge Capital

Stock Markets 13 hours ago (Sep 19, 2019 20:11)

© Reuters. BRIEF-Australian Government Takeovers Panel Declines To Conduct Proceedings On Application On Keybridge Capital Sept 19 (Reuters) - Australian Government Takeovers Panel: * DECLINES TO CONDUCT PROCEEDINGS ON APPLICATION ON KEYBRIDGE CAPITAL FROM BENTLEY CAPITAL, AMONG OTHERS * CONCLUDES NO REASONABLE PROSPECT TO MAKE DECLARATION OF UNACCEPTABLE CIRCUMSTANCES IN RELATION TO APPLICATION
